          <p>We map your current operations, identify bottlenecks, and scope the highest-impact automations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <h4>Design</h4>
          <p>Custom workflow architecture designed around how your business actually runs — not a template.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <h4>Build &amp; Deploy</h4>
          <p>We build every system, integrate your tools, test thoroughly, and deploy in phases so nothing breaks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-num">4</div>
          <h4>Train &amp; Manage</h4>
          <p>Your team gets trained on every system. We stay on as needed to manage, optimize, and scale.</p>
        </div>
